Entities and Attributes
1. ATMContext (State Machine)
CurrentState: current state instance

EnteredPin: user input pin

CurrentUser: reference to active user session

2. UserSession (Mocked User)
AccountNumber: user ID

Pin: current PIN

Balance: current balance

UserName: display name

3. OperationHandler (Chain of Responsibility)
Abstract base for operation types: balance check, withdraw, deposit, PIN change

